    • Method Detail

      • compare

        int compare​(int index0,
            int index1)
        Compare two elements.
        Parameters:
        index0 - the index of the first element
        index1 - the index of the second element
        Returns:
        0 if the elements are equal, less than 0 if the first element comes before the second element, and greater than zero if the first element comes after the second element
